observations.recommendation:
We recommended that the BAC:

Include in the Annual Procurement Plan (APP) the PPAs to be procured during the year with the appropriate mode of procurement;

Require the BAC Secretariat, to post in the PhilGEPS website the Notice of Award, Contract or Purchase Order and Notice to Proceed.

We recommended that the Municipal Health Officer and Municipal Accountant submit the following supporting documents to validate the eligibility and entitlement of the claimants, and to support the completeness, validity and authenticity of the payments:

Original copy of payroll no. 1 in Table 20 duly signed by the Municipal Health Officer that services have been duly rendered;

Pre-determined list by the Local Health Board of the frontline HRHs and HWs, including the BHWs, duly validated by an authorized DOH representative;

Duly accomplished time record of recipients of COVID-19 AHDP and SRA; and

Accomplishment Report for the Job Order and BHWs personnel.

We recommended that the Municipal Health Officer and Municipal Accountant submit the following supporting documents to validate the eligibility and entitlement of the claimants, and to support the completeness, validity and authenticity of the payments:

